data.meta_description: Transform your business through a modern, AI-driven cloud analytics platform. Qlik empowers your entire workforce to make bigger discoveries with data.
data.text:
Leverage the power of cloud analytics and data integration

Transform your business through modern, AI-driven cloud analytics. Qlik empowers your entire workforce to make bigger discoveries and better decisions every day, helping your business become a leader in your industry.

Qlik Sense

Qlik Sense is a cloud analytics platform designed for organizations large and small who are looking for an all-in-one data and analytics solution. With Qlik Sense, you can acquire, transform and visualize data.

Qlik Sense’s key strengths include:

A modern, scalable SaaS deployment model

Outstanding usability and an intuitive interface

Self-service visualizations and interactive dashboards

Search and conversational analytics

Straightforward and powerful web-based authoring

Catalog and data lineage features

Data transformation and automation capabilities

AI and machine learning

You can use Qlik Sense as a standalone solution or embed Qlik visualizations in existing web platforms, leveraging Qlik’s API-driven approach.

Qlik Data Integration

Built right into Qlik SaaS, Qlik Data Integration enables DataOps for any analytics environment. You can accelerate the discovery and availability of real-time, analytics-ready data by automating data streaming, refinement and publishing on any cloud you choose.

Qlik’s outstanding data replication solution provides universal data replication and ingestion capabilities, including change data capture from streaming sources. The Qlik Data Integration platform also provides your organization with the tools to manage data at scale in data warehouses and data lakes.

Get up and running with Qlik

Wipfli is a Qlik Elite Partner, with deep experience in establishing data and analytics solutions. Whether your organization has used Qlik for a long time or is just starting its journey with data, the Qlik platform is an ideal solution to empower your analytics use cases. Wipfli can help you establish your cloud analytics platform in Qlik, train your team and provide ongoing Qlik Managed Services.
